| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3473 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9dde37fb-4ada-5fb2-9f4e-1ccb683d9c85"
